children.subject: It looks like the web app is working now that the EECS servers are back up.

history.content:
Dear Students,

Due to the campus closure and an error in the web application, I have closed access to signing up for Faculty Advising. I opened the system at 10am and many of you have emailed me about the error message you get when you try accessing the web application. This error cannot be fixed right now. Therefore, I have closed the web application and will email all of you once I reopen it - I don't expect to open it today.
I'm signing off from email now, I will respond to emails once campus reopens.
We greatly appreciate your understanding and patience as we try to figure this out.
Best,
Andrea
